{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8b7384fd-1547-4125-9a28-65f2b3eac35a",
    "name": "Selic Pre-Matching API v2.0",
    "description": "Collection para a API do Pre-Matching (Selic Conecta) - versao 2.0.\n\n## Como usar\n1. Importe esta collection e os environments (Sandbox / Producao).\n2. Selecione o Environment desejado (canto superior direito).\n3. Preencha **client_id** e **client_secret** no Environment.\n4. Dispare qualquer request: o token OAuth2 e obtido/renovado automaticamente (pre-request script na collection) e injetado como `Bearer {{access_token}}`.\n\n## Autenticacao\nOAuth2 `client_credentials` (Keycloak, realm `logon`). Endpoint em `{{token_url}}`.\n\n## Variaveis principais (no Environment)\n- `base_url` - base da API (ja inclui `/pre-matching`).\n- `token_url` - endpoint do token OAuth2.\n- `client_id`, `client_secret` - suas credenciais (a unica coisa que o time troca).\n- `access_token`, `access_token_expiry` - gerenciados automaticamente.\n- helpers: `dataMovimento`, `idNegocio`, `idEspecificacao`, `idRequisicao`, `idAssociacao`.\n\n## Rate limit\n100 req/min. Cabecalhos RateLimit-* na resposta; HTTP 429 quando excedido.\n\nFonte: contrato OpenAPI/Swagger oficial e Manual Tecnico de Conectividade (developers.selic.gov.br).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// ===== Auto OAuth2 (client_credentials) =====",
          "// Renova o access_token automaticamente se estiver ausente ou expirado.",
          "// Basta preencher client_id e client_secret no Environment selecionado.",
          "const now = Date.now();",
          "const exp = Number(pm.environment.get(\"access_token_expiry\")) || 0;",
          "const token = pm.environment.get(\"access_token\");",
          "",
          "if (!token || now >= exp) {",
          "  const tokenUrl = pm.environment.get(\"token_url\");",
          "  const clientId = pm.environment.get(\"client_id\");",
          "  const clientSecret = pm.environment.get(\"client_secret\");",
          "",
          "  if (!tokenUrl || !clientId || !clientSecret) {",
          "    console.warn(\"[Selic] Preencha token_url, client_id e client_secret no Environment.\");",
          "  } else {",
          "    pm.sendRequest({",
          "      url: tokenUrl,",
          "      method: \"POST\",",
          "      header: {",
          "        \"Content-Type\": \"application/x-www-form-urlencoded\",",
          "        \"Accept\": \"*/*\"",
          "      },",
          "      body: {",
          "        mode: \"urlencoded\",",
          "        urlencoded: [",
          "          { key: \"grant_type\", value: \"client_credentials\" },",
          "          { key: \"client_id\", value: clientId },",
          "          { key: \"client_secret\", value: clientSecret }",
          "        ]",
          "      }",
          "    }, function (err, res) {",
          "      if (err) { console.error(\"[Selic] Erro ao obter token:\", err); return; }",
          "      let data;",
          "      try { data = res.json(); } catch (e) { console.error(\"[Selic] Token: resposta nao-JSON\"); return; }",
          "      if (data && data.access_token) {",
          "        pm.environment.set(\"access_token\", data.access_token);",
          "        const ttl = (data.expires_in ? data.expires_in : 300) * 1000;",
          "        // renova 15s antes de expirar",
          "        pm.environment.set(\"access_token_expiry\", String(Date.now() + ttl - 15000));",
          "        console.log(\"[Selic] Token OAuth2 renovado.\");",
          "      } else {",
          "        console.error(\"[Selic] Resposta sem access_token:\", data);",
          "      }",
          "    });",
          "  }",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
